FBIS4-6881 "dreas079__a94023" FBIS-EAS-94-079-A Daily Report 25 April 1994 ANNEX Mongolia MPRP Urges End to Hunger Strike MPRP Urges End to Hunger Strike OW2204143094 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1332 GMT 22 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW2204143094 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME English BFN [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 22 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The steering council of the ruling Mongolian People's Revolutionary Party [MPRP] has called upon all the participants of political hunger strike to cease their action. As was said in the appeal, the following reasons should be taken into consideration for ceasing the hunger strikes as the decisions by the council for ensuring the national security, that of the Mongolian parliament as well as out of respect of national traditions and Mongolian statehood.
